                        "id": "18371774920095195",
                        "text": "This place was SO worth it\u2026 I\u2019m still dreaming about their Neve (Parmesan and raw mushroom) pizza \ud83e\udd24 \n\nReservations can be made 2 days in advance from 12pm via TableCheck (just Google 400c Pizza Tokyo), but you have to try and make a reservation right at 12 because slots fill up real quick!! \n\nWhat we ordered: \n\n\ud83c\udf55Neve (twice!!) \u2014 raw mushrooms, Parmesan cheese, liver sauce \n\ud83c\udf55Prosciutto \u2014 prosciutto, tomatoes, mozzarella, arugula \n\ud83c\udf55DOC \u2014 premium Margherita \n\nKids under 6 are not allowed \ud83d\udeab\n\n\ud83d\udccd400c PIZZA TOKYO (Kagurazaka) \n\n#pizza #tokyoeats #tokyofoodie #pizzeria #traveltokyo"
                    }
                }
            ]
